Introduction

API документация для litro.kz

1) Обновить документацию
php artisan scribe:generate

2) Параметры
skip - пропустить (начало 0)
take - количество данных (например 100)
/{skip}/{take} - /0/100 пример (первые 100 записей)

3) Коды ответа HTTP
200 - OK : успешный запрос
400 - Bad Request : неправильный, некорректный запрос
401 - Unauthorized : не авторизован
404 - Not Found : не найдено
500 - Internal Server Error : внутренняя ошибка сервера

Base URL

http://localhost

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

AutoPart - АвтомобильЗапчасти

Получить список - AutoPart

Пример запроса:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://localhost/api/autoPart/get/tempore/perferendis" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/api/autoPart/get/tempore/perferendis"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'http://localhost/api/autoPart/get/tempore/perferendis',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost/api/autoPart/get/tempore/perferendis'
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers)
response.json()

Пример запроса (200):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "count": 0,
    "data": []
}
HTTP ответ:
HTTP ответ ошибка:

    "http://localhost/api/autoPartImage/getByAutoPartId/iure/consequatur/aut"

    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    method: "GET",
    headers,

Создать - Image

Пример запроса:
curl --request POST \
    "http://localhost/api/image/create" \
    --header "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --form "image=@/tmp/phpAiOx3D" 
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/api/image/create"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('image', document.querySelector('input[name="image"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'http://localhost/api/image/create',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'multipart/form-data',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'multipart' => [
            [
                'name' => 'image',
                'contents' => fopen('/tmp/phpAiOx3D', 'r')
            ],
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost/api/image/create'
files = {
  'image': open('/tmp/phpAiOx3D', 'rb')
}
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('POST', url, headers=headers, files=files)
response.json()

Получить данные через UserID - UserProfile

Пример запроса:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://localhost/api/userProfile/getByUserId/ut/optio/voluptatem" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://localhost/api/userProfile/getByUserId/ut/optio/voluptatem"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'http://localhost/api/userProfile/getByUserId/ut/optio/voluptatem',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
import requests
import json

url = 'http://localhost/api/userProfile/getByUserId/ut/optio/voluptatem'
headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  'Accept': 'application/json'
}

response = requests.request('GET', url, headers=headers)
response.json()
